{"tid":2111620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到有泛民願意挨家挨戶咁派防疫物資","createTime":"2020-07-16T15:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T16:08:55.000Z","uid":81236,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b075728ea117e47cc85d550ed6a6ad5c645799","tid":2111620,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"想講<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">真係患難見真章</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母班保皇黨已完唔知去撚左邊<br />\n<br />\n一聽到自己個區有事就縮返入老母個閪窿到<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">無彩攞無曝光唔會係社區上見到佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n更加唔洗望保皇黨會落去疫區派野<br />\n<br />\n雖然蛇齋餅糭就一鑼鑼<br />\n<br />\n但有事一定唔會見人<br />\n<br />\n死左人會就黎自拍話你知佢有關心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢地只會諗打壓，例如諗定叫威露士點解要賣比泛民，點解議員會有錢買<br />\n<br />\n唔會為人著想<br />\n<br />\n然後有錢就話你有油水，完全唔會講保皇把持左社區幾耐，啲油水比哂圍内幾個幫選既人<br />\n<br />\n到選舉就屌起塊閪面去你門口求你投佢，再搭多兩隻糭<br />\n<br />\n仲要你多撚謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再投保皇黨既人既香港人唔止出賣緊自己良心<br />\n<br />\n仲出賣緊自己利益，到有時唔會出現幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54626c82cec7da22b5cc177d890af304628303c3","tid":2111620,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c7091201ec4e52b78805bbb24a8a028b41cf56","tid":2111620,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"本土都一樣縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}